attributes.description: Clear skies signal peace and tranquility
Elves possess unparalleled quartz craftsmanship, through which they imbue their weapons with eternal sharpness
The icy peaks of the Bearish Mountains are said to be home to Elfis whose skin is paler than snow
Traditional ritualistic attire whose yellow color symbolizes the sharing of wisdom
Long hair tied in a bun, to combat the heat of labour. Green in color, often worn by those who experiment with farming
Seeking balance in all things, as with their emotions
Having been through much, few things surprise elves nowadays
Some elves are always suspicious of their surroundings, and can’t be fooled
Headwear is reserved for those with the means and desire to show off
The latest research and innovation allows the wearer to ascertain another’s power level
A subdued style, only an astute eye will notice these earrings are adorned with the rarest gems
